      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que : $\\forall\\ x \\ge -1,\\ \\ln(1+x) \\le x$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ x \\ge -1,\\\n\\ln(1+x) \\le x\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ab732583-136e-4f39-93b9-180d5b59dfc2",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $k \\in {]-1,1[}$. On pose $u_n = (1+k)(1+k^2)\\dots(1+k^n)$.\n    Montrer que la suite $(u_n)$ est convergente\n    (traiter séparément les cas $k \\ge 0$, $k < 0$).",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(k \\in {]-1,1[}\\)</span>. On pose\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(u_n = (1+k)(1+k^2)\\dots(1+k^n)\\)</span>.\nMontrer que la suite <span class=\"math inline\">\\((u_n)\\)</span> est\nconvergente (traiter séparément les cas <span class=\"math inline\">\\(k\n\\ge 0\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(k &lt; 0\\)</span>).</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5a086d84-ed7d-4eed-a33a-d4989eb2ac63",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour $k \\ge 0$, la suite $(u_n)$ est croissante et $\\ln u_n \\le \\frac k{1-k}$.\n\n    Pour $k < 0$, $(u_{2n})$ décro\\^\\i t et converge, et $u_{2n+1} \\sim u_{2n}$.",
        "html": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(k \\ge 0\\)</span>, la suite <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\((u_n)\\)</span> est croissante et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\ln u_n \\le \\frac k{1-k}\\)</span>.</p>\n<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(k &lt; 0\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\((u_{2n})\\)</span> décroı̂t et converge, et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(u_{2n+1} \\sim u_{2n}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
  "preview": "<p>Montrer que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ x \\ge -1,\\\n\\ln(1+x) \\le x\\)</span>.</p>\n"
